  {
    "id": 109,
    "name": "Ali the Oasis-Born",
    "examineText": "A dignified camel who looks insulted by the word livestock.",
    "health": 50,
    "attack": 1,
    "defence": 1,
    "strength": 1,
    "attackSpeed": 5,
    "respawnTime": 100,
    "aggressive": false,
    "wanderRange": 4,
    "size": 2,
    "lootTable": [],
    "modelNpcId": 15,
    "dialogue": {
      "root": "greet",
      "nodes": {
        "greet": {
          "id": "greet",
          "lines": [
            "Peace, traveler. Mind the knees; they are load-bearing miracles.",
            "I am Ali the Oasis-Born, scholar of shade, keeper of snacks, undefeated champion of pretending not to spit."
          ],
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "Any desert wisdom?",
              "next": "wisdom"
            },
            {
              "label": "Why are you by the oasis?",
              "next": "oasis"
            },
            {
              "label": "Are you a camel?",
              "next": "camel"
            },
            {
              "label": "Goodbye."
            }
          ]
        },
        "wisdom": {
          "id": "wisdom",
          "lines": [
            "Drink before you are thirsty. Sit before you are dramatic. Chew before you judge.",
            "Also, never trust a man who says his saddle is only temporary."
          ],
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "Thanks for the wisdom."
            },
            {
              "label": "Goodbye."
            }
          ]
        },
        "oasis": {
          "id": "oasis",
          "lines": [
            "The oasis and I have an arrangement. It provides water; I provide mystery and high-quality chewing.",
            "I also know where the dates fall. A sacred responsibility."
          ],
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "Very important work."
            },
            {
              "label": "Goodbye."
            }
          ]
        },
        "camel": {
          "id": "camel",
          "lines": [
            "Camel? That is what tax collectors call me when they want free transport.",
            "Among friends, I prefer Ali, Lord of the Long Eyelash and Emergency Water."
          ],
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "Apologies, Ali."
            },
            {
              "label": "Goodbye."
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  },
